channel.title: 317 staff panel code?
channel.description:
Is there a code to turn your music tab into a staff panel? It would have things like mute, kick, ban, and ipban. All you would have to do is click the button then enter the person's name. I have seen this before on a server, but I would very much like the code. If anyone has this code, can I please use it? I promise to give you complete credit for it.
Here is how I think it would generally look... (very simple): [img]http://i788.photobucket.com/albums/yy167/alpha_0nix/11.jpg[/img]
